466
00:33:31.440 --> 00:33:34.480
All right, Punchy. You ready
to get bailed out, my friend?

467
00:33:34.760 --> 00:33:36.520
Okay.

468
00:33:37.600 --> 00:33:39.400
Hey, you know
it was a joke, don't you?

469
00:33:39.560 --> 00:33:42.200
Yeah, I know.
You're a very funny guy.

470
00:34:15.600 --> 00:34:17.160
Rocky?

471
00:34:18.080 --> 00:34:20.120
<i>The fans let him know
how they feel about it.</i>

472
00:34:20.280 --> 00:34:22.440
- Excuse me.
