Coming from a human hamper,
that's quite a compliment.

490
00:35:16.720 --> 00:35:18.120
Hide the silverware.

491
00:35:18.320 --> 00:35:19.800
That's nice.

492
00:35:21.680 --> 00:35:22.760
Hey, Spider.

493
00:35:27.360 --> 00:35:29.520
Didn't you knock out
that bum once?

494
00:35:29.680 --> 00:35:31.600
Will you give it a rest?

495
00:35:41.560 --> 00:35:44.720
I'm gonna be late for work for this.
Give me a break, huh?

496
00:35:44.960 --> 00:35:47.600
All right. Just for a few seconds.

497
00:35:47.760 --> 00:35:50.840
<i>In the late '60s, a simulated fight
