508
00:36:18.960 --> 00:36:20.400
Yeah.

509
00:36:20.560 --> 00:36:21.960
<i>A stunning knockout.</i>

510
00:36:22.120 --> 00:36:24.640
<i>Keep in mind, this is taking
the human factor out of it.</i>

511
00:36:24.840 --> 00:36:26.560
<i>- The computer says Balboa...
- Beautiful.</i>

512
00:36:26.720 --> 00:36:31.320
<i>... would be triumphant, KO 13.
