521
00:36:52.440 --> 00:36:54.320
<i>What's the specialty,
pounded chicken?</i>

522
00:36:54.480 --> 00:36:57.800
<i>Anyway, I would have paid to see
the fight. Next topic, NAS CAR...</i>

523
00:36:58.000 --> 00:36:59.800
<i>... and the controversy
